name: Nella Domenici
email: nella@nellaforsenate.com
subject: TOMORROW: Join us in Socorro to help get out the vote!
body: https://www.nellaforsenate.com/ Dear Team Nella, Don’t forget, this Saturday, November 2nd, we need your help to make a real difference as we approach Election Day! Join me and Rebecca Dow in Socorro as we work towards connecting with voters to bring a New Day to New Mexico. 📞 Phone Banking & Door Knocking with Rebecca Dow 🕘 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM 📍 Socorro County Republican Party, 115 B California St, Socorro, NM 🔗 RSVP HERE: Get Out the Vote Rally (https://www.nellaforsenate.com/event-details/join-nella-domenici-and-rebecca-dow-in-socorro-county) 🕔 5:00 PM - 7:00 PM 📍 New Mexico Tech Golf Course, 1 Canyon Road, Socorro, NM This is part of our final push, and every conversation and connection matters. We need your energy, your passion, and your dedication to help bring about the change New Mexico deserves. Let’s finish strong and ensure that every voice is heard!
